& [InferenceJobResult] is evidence review proposal
  + [capture] is worker claim that local model is ready for all SOP jobs because it passed one isolated prompt
  + [evidence] is single isolated prompt success with no additional tests or metrics
  + [outside] is lack of external validation or benchmark data
  + [integration_status] is not integrated into any workflow yet
  + [caution] is risk of overgeneralizing from limited evidence
  + [revise] is add comprehensive testing, validation, and external benchmarks before integration
  + [next_step] is conduct broader test suite and gather external benchmark results
